value.name: Dungeons & Dragons
value.overview: Six friends are transported into the Dungeons & Dragons realm and must try to find a way home with the help of their guide 'Dungeon Master'.

value.name: Epic NPC Man: Dungeons & Dragons
value.overview: Rowan, Adam, Alan and Britt (dungeon master Robert) play D&D. The four players play as their characters from Epic NPC Man, with whatever happens to the characters being deemed as canon in the Epic NPC Man universe.

value.name: Dungeons & Dragons: The Forgotten Realms
value.overview: Live-action series adaptation of Hasbro's popular Dungeons & Dragons fantasy role-playing game franchise.
